      "created_at": "2016-10-05T17:34:18.360Z",
      "cooked": "<p>vetem se muzika e sfondit apo ndonje stimul tjeter pamor-auditiv do te ule perqendrimin tend tek studimi. rekomandohet sa me pak multitasking kur studiohet. <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/wink.png?v=5\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wink:\"></p>",
