      "username": "Momo",
      "name": "",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/peshkupauje.com/momo/{size}/217_2.png",
      "created_at": "2016-10-05T17:38:37.184Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ne fakt tani jam duke bere nje proces pak a shume mekanik. Po bej nje permbledhje te librit. Kur studioj (lexoj permbledhjen) nuk degjoj me muzike, madje ve edhe tapa qe te bllokoj cdo zhurme <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/smiley.png?v=5\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smiley:\"></p>\n<p>Zakonisht kur bej keto permbledhjet, degjoj kete (apo te ngjashme me kete):</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WPni755-Krg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WPni755-Krg</a></p>",
