      "created_at": "2016-10-11T12:14:57.629Z",
      "cooked": "<p>“Bum bum bum” se pse me duket se e ka me hile me neve. Mesazh anti-racist (white dog that breeds), i cili ne fakt kthehet e behet serish racist ne ekstremin tjeter, i percjelle permes tingujve te tille (sh like), sikur s’nuk… them une. Po kush e di…<br>\nFlm per njohjen me Leisure, Fear less, Ill wind.</p>",
